    <div>
        <div class="rounded-1" >
            <div class="text-center">
                <p>
                    Studio Briefcase is a free-to-use library dedicated to introducing new users to programming
                    languages and frameworks in a way to overcome learning curve in the most time efficient, 
                    frustrating free manner possible. This website works by meticulously hyperlinking learners to 
                    relevant documentation and other content creators.
                </p>
                <p><strong>Donations will primarily be used for the following puruposes.</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
     
        <div>
