                        <p>
                            The upkeep of third party services in Azure and GitHub and continued level of security to keep
                            StudioBriefcase safe.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col text-center rounded-1">
                    <div>
                        <h5>Connecting Community and Creators</h5>
                        <p>
                            Building an environemt to connect like minded peers and other tutorial creators. This
                            isn't a site that seeks to compete, but one that brings people together.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col text-center rounded-1">
                    <div>
                        <h5>Continued Development</h5>
                        <p>
                            Completing Tutorial Content and Expanding the range of topics in the library. A continued
                            dedication to save time and frustration.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>


            </div>
        </div>
       
    </div>


